    • level

      public int level()
      Beschreibung aus Schnittstelle kopiert: ReceivedReward
      Returns the level the player received the reward for.
      For milestone rewards, this is always the level the player has unlocked the reward.
      For interval rewards, this is the level the player has received the reward for. So if a reward is applied with an interval of 1 (each level), the player is level 50, and the player has received the reward at level 10, the reward is applied for each from 10 to 50.
      Angegeben von:
      level in Schnittstelle ReceivedReward
      Gibt zurück:
      level
